' CROSS-LAYER RELATIONSHIPS
' ============================================================

' Controller → Model
CircuitController --> CircuitModel : owns & mutates

' Canvas → Controller (Observer)
CircuitCanvasView --> CircuitController : registers as observer

' Canvas → Pathfinder
WireGraphicsItem ..> IDAStarPathfinder : lazy import for routing
_ComponentAdapter ..> IDAStarPathfinder : obstacle data
_WireAdapter ..> IDAStarPathfinder : obstacle data

' Theme usage
CircuitCanvasView ..> ThemeManager : colors, pens, fonts
ComponentGraphicsItem ..> ThemeManager : component colors
WireGraphicsItem ..> ThemeManager : wire colors
AnnotationItem ..> ThemeManager : text colors

' Simulation flow
SimulationController --> CircuitModel : reads for netlist

